    public class MainWindow
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    This class represents the main window of the application. It shows a navigation tree on the left side and a panel on the right side as well as a menu bar. The nav tree is represented by the NavTree class. The panel on the right side is called view in the application and may be set using the methods provided by this class.
